trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder.Quality> category specifies the level of compression for an image.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder.Quality>分類都會指定映像的壓縮層級。

trans-unit.source: When used to construct an <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.EncoderParameter>, the range of useful values for the quality category is from 0 to 100.
trans-unit.target: 當用來建構<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.EncoderParameter>，品質分類有用的值範圍是從 0 到 100。

trans-unit.source: The lower the number specified, the higher the compression and therefore the lower the quality of the image.
trans-unit.target: 低指定的數字，愈高壓縮和影像品質因此會降低。

trans-unit.source: Zero would give you the lowest quality image and 100 the highest.
trans-unit.target: 最低品質的影像和 100，零會提供您最高。

trans-unit.target: 程式碼會將影像旋轉 90 度，並將它儲存在個別的 JPEG 檔案。

trans-unit.source: Represents an <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder" /> object that is initialized with the globally unique identifier for the version parameter category.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder" /> 物件，此物件使用版本參數分類的全域唯一識別項來進行初始化。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder.Quality> category specifies the level of compression for an image.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder.Quality>分類都會指定映像的壓縮層級。

trans-unit.source: When used to construct an <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.EncoderParameter>, the range of useful values for the quality category is from 0 to 100.
trans-unit.target: 當用來建構<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.EncoderParameter>，品質分類有用的值範圍是從 0 到 100。

trans-unit.source: The lower the number specified, the higher the compression and therefore the lower the quality of the image.
trans-unit.target: 低指定的數字，愈高壓縮和影像品質因此會降低。

trans-unit.source: Zero would give you the lowest quality image and 100 the highest.
trans-unit.target: 最低品質的影像和 100，零會提供您最高。

trans-unit.source: When you pass a parameter to an image encoder, the parameter is encapsulated in an <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.EncoderParameter> object.
trans-unit.target: 當您將參數傳遞至影像編碼器時，參數會封裝在<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.EncoderParameter>物件。

trans-unit.source: One of the fields of the <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.EncoderParameter> object is a GUID that specifies the category of the parameter.
trans-unit.target: 其中一個欄位的<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.EncoderParameter>物件是指定之參數的分類的 GUID。

trans-unit.source: Use the static fields of the <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder> class to retrieve an <xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder> that contains parameters of the desired category.
trans-unit.target: 使用的靜態欄位<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder>類別來擷取<xref:System.Drawing.Imaging.Encoder>包含所需的類別目錄的參數。

trans-unit.source: The image encoders that are built into [!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)] receive parameters that belong to several categories.
trans-unit.target: 內建的影像編碼器[!INCLUDE[ndptecgdiplus](~/includes/ndptecgdiplus-md.md)]接收隸屬於數種類別的參數。

trans-unit.target: 下表列出所有類別目錄，且每個分類相關聯的 GUID。
